@startuml buttons
skinparam StateBackgroundColor #f5f5f5
skinparam StateBorderColor #666
skinparam ArrowColor #333
skinparam DefaultFontName monospace

title buttonTick() — state machine

[*] --> IDLE

IDLE --> TRACKING : pressed\n(record pressedAt)

TRACKING --> IDLE : released within DEBOUNCE_MS\n/ BTN_NONE
TRACKING --> TRACKING : held < LONG_PRESS_MS\n/ BTN_NONE
TRACKING --> LONG_HELD : held ≥ LONG_PRESS_MS\n/ BTN_LONG_PRESS (once)
TRACKING --> IDLE : released ≥ DEBOUNCE_MS and < LONG_PRESS_MS\n/ BTN_SHORT_PRESS

LONG_HELD --> LONG_HELD : held further\n/ BTN_NONE
LONG_HELD --> IDLE : released\n/ BTN_NONE

note right of TRACKING
  elapsed = now - pressedAt
  unsigned subtraction handles
  millis() rollover safely
end note

note right of LONG_HELD
  longFired = true prevents
  BTN_LONG_PRESS from firing
  again on subsequent ticks
end note
@enduml
